            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": false,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* NASA Science enjoys strong bipartisan support, as evidenced by the funding restoration led by Reps. Bacon and Chu in FY 2026\n* Space science represents less than one-third of one percent of federal spending while delivering massive returns in national prestige\n* Programmatic stability is required to protect the workforce pipeline of next-generation STEM professionals and entrepreneurs",
